4YyNXZq43z","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec1jaFE0M4y5HEIV","target":"recFinINtrGjUmVDi","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec1jaFE0M4y5HEIV","target":"recaHkhAvEICQr7fB","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec1jaFE0M4y5HEIV","target":"recpqKANUDcRgN4HU","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec1jaFE0M4y5HEIV","target":"recirR7tLEeni78L3","label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"recW2BdtRrMthJCsC","ref":"Ps.87.1","text":"His foundation is in the holy mountains."},{"id":"recAJfFfkiFeAGXW2","ref":"Ps.87.2","text":"The LORD loveth the gates of Zion more than all the dwellings of Jacob."},{"id":"recZsK5w1Ye0VPodI","ref":"Ps.87.3","text":"Glorious things are spoken of thee, O city of God. Selah."},{"id":"recVrz8LvVNtUy5UO","ref":"Ps.87.4","text":"I will make mention of Rahab and Babylon to them that know me: behold Philistia, and Tyre, with Ethiopia; this man was born there."},{"id":"recGkoI6FZ8TLacAk","ref":"Ps.87.5","text":"And of Zion it shall be said, This and that man was born in her: and the highest himself shall establish her."},{"id":"reci0a8h5pU0a3n7p","ref":"Ps.87.6","text":"The LORD shall count, when he writeth up the people, that this man was born there. Selah."},{"id":"recshvBK23Pw7wPRr","ref":"Ps.87.7","text":"As well the singers as the players on instruments shall be there: all my springs are in thee."}]}
